@Node DoorsCalled "Doors Called"

  Doors Called
  ============

    MAIL_ADD - Called so that a message can be posted.  The following
    parameters are used:

      "<weekfinalfilename> TO ALL FROM <node sysopaccount> TYPE P
      SUBJECT -=[ WeekTop for week commencing <weekstartdate> ]=-"

